# =============================================================================
# Tips
# =============================================================================

# 1. Use 'set -xg' for global environment variables
# 2. Use 'set -Ux' for universal variables (persist across sessions)
# 3. Use 'abbr -a' to add abbreviations
# 4. Test changes with: source local/config.fish.local
# 5. See current variables: set -xg
# 6. See current abbreviations: abbr -s
# 7. Use fish_config for interactive configuration

